# Design System Decision Document

> **Purpose:**  
> This document records all key design system decisions for the website, ensuring consistency, clarity, and a shared reference for all designers and developers.

## 1. Brand & Visual Identity

### 1.1. Brand Values & Tone of Voice

- **Brand Values:**  
  _Describe the core values the design should communicate (e.g., trust, innovation, friendliness)._
- **Tone of Voice:**  
  _Describe the tone for all written content (e.g., formal, conversational, playful, authoritative)._
- **Logo Usage:**  
  _Guidelines for logo placement, sizing, and clear space._

